rows.label: tlk003501_02_msg0001
rows.name:
You know, Invidian food may not look
appetizing, but it's actually damn tasty.

rows.label: tlk003501_02_msg0002
rows.name:
And there's nothing better than a swig
of Jenerossi Tea after a good meal.

rows.label: tlk003501_02_msg0003
rows.name:
What? You think elegantly sipping
tea doesn't suit me?

rows.label: tlk003501_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm a bit like Invidian food myself.
I may not look it, but I'm pretty refined
when you get to know me!
